org.gbif.api.model.registry

Class DatasetOccurrenceDownloadUsage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.api.model.registry.DatasetOccurrenceDownloadUsage

  • public class DatasetOccurrenceDownloadUsage
extends Object
    Represents the information about the usage of one dataset in an occurrence download. Provides information about the number of records that the dataset provided to the download; additionally, provide the references to the download and dataset entities.
